items.name: smart-dustbin
items.description: This project is a Smart Dustbin simulation developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It demonstrates the concept of an automatic, touch-free dustbin that opens its lid when a user approaches and closes it after a short delay. The project helps beginners understand automation concepts and basic front-end development.
